sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as 客户端应用
    participant ResourceOwner as 资源所有者(用户)
    participant AuthorizationServer as 授权服务器
    participant ResourceServer as 资源服务器
    
    ResourceOwner->>Client: 使用客户端应用
    Client->>ResourceOwner: 重定向到授权页面
    ResourceOwner->>AuthorizationServer: 登录并授权
    AuthorizationServer->>ResourceOwner: 返回授权码
    ResourceOwner->>Client: 传递授权码
    Client->>AuthorizationServer: 请求访问令牌(含授权码)
    AuthorizationServer->>Client: 验证并返回访问令牌
    Client->>ResourceServer: 使用访问令牌请求资源
    ResourceServer->>AuthorizationServer: 验证令牌(可选)
    ResourceServer->>Client: 返回受保护资源